com.siperian.sif.message.mrm

Class AuthenticateResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.SiperianResponse
      • com.siperian.sif.message.mrm.AuthenticateResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class AuthenticateResponse
extends SiperianResponse
    Represents the response to the AuthenticateRequest object. The AuthenticateResponse object provides methods to get a list of user roles to which the user belongs, the password expiration date, and the status that indicates whether an external authentication mechanism is used.

    See Also:
    AuthenticateRequest, Serialized Form

    API Pair: AuthenticateRequest

    API Group: User Management
